theorem
Th62: (((( -infty ) < x & x < ( +infty )) & x <> ( 0 )) implies ( |. x .| * |. ( ( 1. ) / x ) .| ) = ( 1. ))
proof
assume that
A1: (( -infty ) < x & x < ( +infty ))
and
A2: x <> ( 0 );
reconsider a = x as Real by A1,XXREAL_0:14;
A3: ( ( 1. ) / x ) = ( 1 / a ) by EXTREAL1:2,MESFUNC1:def 8;
